# Environment configuration for Battle frontend
#
# DEVELOPMENT USAGE:
#   Do NOT set VITE_API_URL for local development.
#   Leave it commented out — the Vite dev server proxy (/api → http://localhost:3000)
#   handles API routing server-side. This works for both:
#     - localhost browser access (npm run dev)
#     - network/mobile access (npm run dev:mobile, accessed via LAN IP or QR code)
#
# PRODUCTION USAGE:
#   Uncomment and set VITE_API_URL to your deployed backend URL.
#
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend.example.com/api
